column5: So, I guess it was a combination of my snooping and my wife really wanting to give me my present, but today I got my present! My wonderful wife gave me a new Canon Rebel XS DSLR, which also came with a Canon photoprinter....so i'm all set. All i have to do is start getting out!  Dave
Great stuff Dave You must of been a good boy for getting an early Christmas present Like you said get out and post good pics for us Leechman
I'm hoping Santa brings me one of those too     You sure he didn't go to the wrong house  Awesome camera bud!!  Joey
